01:01:58.302 --> 01:02:00.203
This is not the first time
that this has happened...

01:02:00.337 --> 01:02:01.471
- He's crazy.
- Get back.

01:02:01.605 --> 01:02:03.273
Get back.
Over there.

01:02:03.407 --> 01:02:05.642
I'm sorry, sir.
W... what's your name?

01:02:05.776 --> 01:02:06.810
Robert.

01:02:07.110 --> 01:02:09.513
