01:08:16.613 --> 01:08:18.814
spreading through your body...

01:08:21.953 --> 01:08:24.520
and then the rot will start.

01:08:30.294 --> 01:08:33.898
Why don't you come out
and fight while you still can?

01:08:37.834 --> 01:08:39.769
Yeah, I'll play fair.

01:09:00.191 --> 01:09:01.892
It's loaded.

01:09:06.397 --> 01:09:09.666
You have one minute...

01:09:11.734 --> 01:09:13.170
to try and grab it...

01:09:15.439 --> 01:09:16.606
starting...

01:09:17.540 --> 01:09:18.707
now.

01:09:22.880 --> 01:09:24.982
Are you too scared?

01:09:27.684 --> 01:09:30.187
You know the one thing
I can't stand?

01:09:34.024 --> 01:09:35.091
Cowards!

01:09:40.096 --> 01:09:43.666
