to take care of something.

01:30:55.838 --> 01:30:58.942
<i>Are you there? Sam!</i>

01:31:00.778 --> 01:31:03.247
<i>Sam, are you there?</i>

01:31:03.813 --> 01:31:05.115
<i>Sam!</i>

01:31:05.916 --> 01:31:07.017
